caption.title: Gel electrophoresis analysis of RT-PCR products.
caption.p: According to the results from gel electrophoresis analysis of different samples given in the figure, there are 34 RT-PCR products; the sizes of the amplicons (ID 2–40, 3–44, 4–49, 5–141, and 6–146) are consistent with DENV-2, while the rest are consistent with DENV-1.
